description.value:
Dooge is a Cardano-based meme token created to bring love and support to dogs in need. Just like a spring, each Dooge coin extends its help to every corner, supporting stray dogs and promoting responsible pet ownership. 

In the future, a portion of Dooge tokens will be dedicated to funding stray dog welfare and advocating for better dog care knowledge. Join our community of passionate dog lovers and help make a difference together.
